title: Central Catholic's Anna Younger is lehighvalleylive Girls Soccer Player of Week
text:
Anna Younger of Central Catholic is the lehighvalleylive Girls Soccer Player of the Week. (lehighvalleylive file photo) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on September 30, 2015 10:00 AM 
GIRLS SOCCER PLAYER OF THE WEEK Anna Younger (Courtesy Photo ) 
Anna Younger , Central Catholic 
Younger scored three goals in the Vikings' 4-0 win over Northampton on Monday. 
The senior forward has seven goals and three assists since last Tuesday. Younger has at least one goal in her last four games. 
She has 14 goals and six assists on the season. 
HONORABLE MENTION: Jr. M Haven Snyder , Nazareth; Sr. F Katelyn Lauziere , Warren Hills; Jr. F Jaiden Coyne , Freedom; So. M Emma Terefenko , Central Catholic; Sr. M Lauren Binn , Saucon Valley; Sr. M Monica Wood , Palmerton; Sr. F Ivanna Jones , Whitehall; Sarah Hathaway , Northwestern.
